==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superficialize
<hw>Su`per*fi"cial*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
attend to, or to treat, superficially, or in a shallow or slighting
way.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is a characteristic weakness of the day to
<qex>superficialize</qex> evil.</q> <rj><qau>E. P.
Whipple.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superficiary</ent>⟦br⟧
